OL,3,CNottinghamshire business fined after
OL,4,Ctwo workers injured in explosion
OL,6,FA Nottinghamshire company has been
OL,7,Ffined after an explosion caused two
OL,8,Femployees to suffer life-changing
OL,9,Finjuries
OL,11,FBio Dynamic Ltd in Colwick has been
OL,12,Ffined #304,500 and ordered to pay
OL,13,Fcosts to HSE & Environment Agency of
OL,14,F#229,987.
OL,16,FOn 20 September 2017, two workers were
OL,17,Fusing a grinder to cut and replace
OL,18,Fpipework at the top of an 11 metre
OL,19,Fhigh metal tank containing waste
OL,20,Fslurry. They were not using harnesses.
