OL,4,Ctwo workers injured in explosion
OL,6,FSparks from the grinder ignited
OL,7,Fflammable gases causing the tank to
OL,8,Fexplode. The tank projected high into
OL,9,Fthe air before crashing to the ground.
OL,11,FThe company produces electricity from
OL,12,Ffood waste by anaerobic digestion. It
OL,13,Fsays it's 'grateful that this matter
OL,14,Fhas finally been brought to a close'
OL,15,Fand 'extend its deepest sympathies to
OL,16,Fboth Mr Tyrko and Mr Patek'.
