OL,3,CNottinghamshire business fined after
OL,4,Ctwo workers injured in explosion
OL,6,FTomasz Patek was flung out of the
OL,7,Fmobile elevating work platform (MEWP)
OL,8,Finto the air and landed on the ground
OL,9,Fin the slurry around the tank. He
OL,10,Fsuffered serious injuries to his back,
OL,11,Fhead and torso and was in hospital for
OL,12,Ftwo months. His injuries were so
OL,13,Fsevere that he was not able to work
OL,14,Ffor more than two years.
