OL,6,FTomasz suffers from pre and post-
OL,7,Ftraumatic amnesia and has no specific
OL,8,Frecollection of the events. In a
OL,9,Fstatement, he reveals the
OL,10,Fpsychological scars from the incident;
OL,11,F"After the accident, I was unable to
OL,12,Frecover emotionally.
OL,14,F"I did not realise what had happened
OL,15,Fand was in deep shock. I could not
OL,16,Fcope with the pain. I could not accept
OL,17,Fan accident had happened to me."
OL,19,FRobert Tyrko was thrown into the air
OL,20,Fand landed back in the basket of the
OL,21,FMEWP.
