OL,6,FIn his statement, Robert explains how
OL,7,Fthe explosion has affected his day-to-
OL,8,Fday life; "This whole situation is
OL,9,Fhaving a huge impact on my
OL,10,Frelationship. I can't help my wife in
OL,11,Fanything like I used to be able to.
OL,12,FMagda is both wife and husband because
OL,13,Fall my responsibilities fell on her;
OL,14,Falong with the kids.
OL,16,F"Also my personality is explosive. I
OL,17,Flose my patience very quickly. I
OL,18,Fattended appointments with a
OL,19,Fpsychologist because I had nightmares
OL,20,Fthat I was still having this accident."
