OL,6,FA joint investigation by the Health
OL,7,Fand Safety Executive (HSE) and the
OL,8,FEnvironment Agency found that the
OL,9,Fcompany had failed to ensure the
OL,10,Fhealth and safety of its employees and
OL,11,Fothers nearby.
OL,13,FThe company had kept and treated waste
OL,14,Fin a manner likely to cause pollution
OL,15,Fto the environment. The explosion was
OL,16,Fcaused by multiple failures in the
OL,17,Fcompany's management system and
OL,18,Fexacerbated by multiple breaches of
OL,19,Fthe company's environmental permit.
