OL,6,FAt a hearing at Nottingham Crown Court
OL,7,Fon 22 November 2024, Bio Dynamic (UK)
OL,8,FLimited, of Colwick Industrial Estate,
OL,9,FNottingham:
OL,11,FAfter the hearing, HSE inspector
OL,12,FRichenda Dixon said: "It's remarkable
OL,13,Fthat Robert and Tomasz weren't killed.
OL,15,F"This incident resulted from
OL,16,Ffundamental and multiple failings by
OL,17,Fthe company to properly manage its
OL,18,Fhealth and safety risks.
