OL,6,FSenior Environmental Crime Officer
OL,7,FIain Regan said: "This was a lengthy
OL,8,Fand technically complex investigation
OL,9,Fby the Environment Agency and the HSE
OL,10,Fduring which we found that the
OL,11,Fcompany's attitude towards
OL,12,Fenvironmental compliance was largely
OL,13,Fcosmetic. Although the site had an
OL,14,Fenvironmental permit, the company was
OL,15,Fnot complying with the conditions of
OL,16,Fthe permit or with their own
OL,17,Fmanagement system and procedures.
