OL,6,F"Sites which receive, treat or dispose
OL,7,Fof waste must be permitted to ensure
OL,8,Fthat they minimise the risk to the
OL,9,Fenvironment or human health. Incidents
OL,10,Fsuch as the explosion at Bio Dynamic
OL,11,Fshow why it is essential that such
OL,12,Fsites strictly comply with all the
OL,13,Fconditions of their environmental
OL,14,Fpermit and take their environmental
OL,15,Fresponsibilities seriously. The
OL,16,Fconsequences of the company's failure
OL,17,Fto comply with its environmental
OL,18,Fpermit could have been fatal. As it
OL,19,Fis, two employees have been left with
OL,20,Flife changing physical and mental
OL,21,Finjuries which continue to devastate
OL,22,Ftheir lives seven years on from this
OL,23,Fincident."
